						<div class="postbody">I've got a parallax effect in one level of my new game. It works perfectly on emulators and on the original NES. But on AVS, after the second split the scroll kind of jitters up and down. I'm experimenting with ways to nudge the scroll update so that it aligns more correctly with hblank, but I can't seem to get it perfect on AVS. I either get scroll bounce, or a small glitch (similar to the status bar glitch in SMB3).</div>

					
